{"tid":597302,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有無經歷過回魂夜？","createTime":"2018-03-18T13:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T14:27:26.000Z","uid":36097,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5f695ffb05940dfc5f1f0644bfbd2993dfdad763","tid":597302,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"我婆婆走果年我得十歲<br />\n夜晚我自己訓，我記得當晚好凍<br />\n冬天得返4-5度，凍到我係咁震<br />\n想攞多張被但又起唔到身，<br />\n矇矇矓矓見到婆婆走埋黎我幫我come被，即時暖返哂，<br />\n婆婆臨走時仲掃下我頭，<br />\n我就喊到豬頭咁拉住婆婆唔俾佢走，<br />\n果時我仲以為發夢。<br />\n點知我訓醒見到自己多左2張被<br />\n（訓前一張羽絨被）<br />\n我媽仲問我幾時入過佢房攞被，點解佢唔知<br />\n我話係婆婆幫我come，<br />\n之後我媽問我點樣見到婆婆，我一路講佢聽我媽就一路喊到豬頭咁"},{"pid":"c96b62c21db8c53e544f6cba1b18536673172f11","tid":597302,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bff015627d8c58f2c0801ac32eef22b33fef98","tid":597302,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bffefbabf8a9db564d64a37af1236197f5efa41","tid":597302,"uid":74262,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d0481b77fe04e37dc03805f3831f14cd930c5f0","tid":597302,"uid":27511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"Yes. 好彩準備左朱古力同保鮮紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cace5c46dedd5df315fe9b485940f236111ae50f","tid":597302,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"屋企老人家會灑麵粉響門口"},{"pid":"1af592ed35e241ffe1f7707135e3febbcfcd5e3d","tid":597302,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"好想試下裝cam睇下回魂情況"},{"pid":"7fcbc624c40a06b2f6939ad41c734dbcf2cf6194","tid":597302,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc